# VHS tape — second README demo: multi-chain contract lookup.
# Render with:  vhs docs/assets/demo2.tape
# Output:       docs/assets/demo2.gif

Output docs/assets/demo2.gif

Set Theme "nord"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 940
Set Height 520
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 24
Set TypingSpeed 1ms
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "clear && python3 docs/assets/demo2.py"
Enter
Show
Sleep 18s
